WEBVTT

00:02.568 --> 00:05.809
A horse and an ass were travelling together.

00:06.568 --> 00:09.771
The ass carried a heavy load on its back.

00:12.204 --> 00:15.397
"I wish I were you," sighed the ass.

00:16.176 --> 00:20.990
The ass wanted to be like the horse because it had no load.

00:24.495 --> 00:31.165
Next day, however, there was a great battle, and the horse was fatally wounded.

00:32.047 --> 00:36.305
The ass was happy not to be the horse after all.

